Boss, one bowl of noodles.

3
00:00:23,519 --> 00:00:25,239
How much for a lamb skewer?

4
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,719
Take the shrimp.

5
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:29,440
Too many people in line. Forget it.

6
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:33,120
No need for that.

7
00:00:34,679 --> 00:00:36,159
Sausage shop in the southwest.

8
00:00:36,159 --> 00:00:37,159
Little Fish No.6 spotted!

9
00:00:37,759 --> 00:00:39,039
Don't rush!

10
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:41,439
Look for Big Fish.
Big Fish is the main target.

11
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:42,719
Roger that.

12
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,479
Weixiang, The Eye shows up.

13
00:00:54,479 --> 00:00:55,320
Stay sharp.

14
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:56,159
Take it slow.

15
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:56,799
Thank you.

16
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,200
Mentor, goods are delivered.

17
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,439
The Eye is on it now.

18
00:01:26,528 --> 00:01:27,200
Get out.

19
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,239
- Let's go.
- Okay.

20
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,239
This tastes good.

21
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,599
Are you alright?

22
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,760
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

23
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,400
Little Fish got it.
Boss, should we act?

24
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,920
Mentor, should we act?

25
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,799
They're going to run!

26
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,439
Arrest them!

27
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,000
Come on.

28
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,759
Where to go?

29
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,400
Stop!

30
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,400
Don't move.

31
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,759
- Hand over the child!
- What do you want?

32
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:12,639
My child is snatched!

33
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,719
My child is snatched!

34
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,759
We are police!

35
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,439
Everyone, please cooperate.

36
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,319
Go.

37
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,599
You, over there.

38
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:29,039
We are police!

39
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,840
Sorry.

40
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,120
Stop.

41
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:34,520
Stop there!

42
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,039
Keep running. Quite a runner, huh?

43
00:02:41,312 --> 00:02:41,960
Squat down!

44
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,439
Mentor, we caught three Little Fish.

45
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:50,240
(Welcome to Night Market)
Make way!

46
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,479
Go, don't dawdle.

47
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,159
Get in the car quickly.

48
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,439
There is a pregnant woman

49
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,479
with a kid.

50
00:03:29,504 --> 00:03:30,319
Mission complete.

51
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,719
Stop staring.

52
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:34,960
Stop staring.

53
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:29,152
=Endless Protection=

54
00:05:29,824 --> 00:05:32,448
=Episode 4=

55
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:42,112
(Yang's Restaurant)

56
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:43,968
(Hiring Assistant Cook)
(Closed)

57
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,959
You are back.

58
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,480
Been closed for over a month, huh?

59
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,759
My wife and I came a few times,

60
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:55,759
but the shop was closed.

61
00:05:55,872 --> 00:05:56,839
(Closed)
It is closed.

62
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,079
Wait!

63
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,319
Mr. Yang.

64
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,160
My wife is pregnant.

65
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,199
She vomits everything,

66
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,439
and only wants your porridge.

67
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,199
Whatever semi-prepared food

68
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,480
you have now,

69
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:07,439
just pack it.

70
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,759
I'll cook myself.

71
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:11,079
- Have a seat.
- Okay.

72
00:06:15,635 --> 00:06:18,080
(Hiring Assistant Cook)

73
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:26,639
The number you dialed is powered off.

74
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,519
Please try again later.

75
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,040
Sorry, the number you dialed
is powered off.

76
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:39,136
(Why are you not answering?)

77
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,360
Thank you!

78
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,839
Thank you so much.

79
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,560
We're really short-staffed

80
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:55,759
and you're so urgent.

81
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,279
These are all ingredients.

82
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,360
But I've written

83
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,399
the recipes on paper.

84
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,959
There's also ginger milk,
helping with morning sickness.

85
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:05,560
Take this.

86
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,560
It's my gratitude.

87
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,480
Don't have change.

88
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:08,920
Really.

89
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,000
Chef took all my money when he left.

90
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:13,560
Just accept it.

91
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,519
That's really unfortunate for you.

92
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,040
Well...

93
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:18,040
Why not report to the police?

94
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,199
What's the point?

95
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:20,160
Everyone suffers.

96
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,759
I'll redecorate it.

97
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:25,720
Come by more often then.

98
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,319
Sure.

99
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,920
- Close the door.
- Okay.

100
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,480
He is really nice.

101
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,199
Take a couple of sips.

102
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,959
Try this. Come on.

103
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,399
What's wrong?

104
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:52,360
What's wrong? Gone bad?

105
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,199
No.

106
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:54,959
Take it away!

107
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:55,879
What's wrong?

108
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,399
Take it away!

109
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:58,839
Okay, okay. Don't take it.

110
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,759
Alright.

111
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:01,800
That's okay.

112
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,240
Alright.

113
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:05,199
That's okay.

114
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:08,480
I still have seven
or eight months to go.

115
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,279
How will I get through this?

116
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:12,480
I'm feeling so uncomfortable.

117
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:14,639
Alright, I know it.

118
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:17,040
You don't need to do anything!

119
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,360
You are just speaking!

120
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:22,560
When I had prenatal checkups,

121
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,720
you didn't show up.

122
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,120
I filed a record alone.

123
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,879
Others husbands

124
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,240
all accompanied their wives.

125
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:31,160
Where did you go?

126
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,279
Where were you?

127
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:34,159
I was wrong.

128
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,080
I'll accompany you.

129
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,320
It's been ten years.

130
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:41,360
I wait at home for you every day.

131
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,519
Now we have a child.

132
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:47,919
Will we both wait for you at home?

133
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,840
No.

134
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,360
I'll wait for you.

135
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,600
I'll wait for you and our kid.

136
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:52,519
I'll wait for you.

137
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:54,120
I'll run straight home after work.

138
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,440
I promise, okay?

139
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,759
Alright.

140
00:08:59,519 --> 00:08:59,960
Come in.

141
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,279
What is the matter?

142
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,679
Nothing important.

143
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,399
I...

144
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:18,200
Just water your flowers

145
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:21,039
and see if you have any instructions.

146
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,879
My flowers don't need tea.

147
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,480
Flowers don't, but you do.

148
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,279
I'll pour it for you.

149
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,039
Just say it.

150
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,240
I...

151
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,279
I just want to ask if

152
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,039
the personnel from Procuratorate

153
00:09:47,039 --> 00:09:49,679
come to visit here again?

154
00:09:50,784 --> 00:09:51,639
Be straightforward.

155
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,519
Any news about my interview
of Procuratorate?

156
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,399
Bai.

157
00:09:59,759 --> 00:10:02,000
Are you really a lubber?

158
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,960
You offended Procuratorate leaders

159
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,320
so harshly.

160
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:08,120
Still expect them to hire you?

161
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,240
No.

162
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:10,440
I just thought

163
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,360
if it doesn't work out,

164
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,720
I'll just work hard

165
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,480
and follow you.

166
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,039
Then, just work hard.

167
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,000
Chief, you're well-informed.

168
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:25,279
Are there any internal transfers

169
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:29,320
in other departments
before the New Year?

170
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,159
Bai.

171
00:10:35,759 --> 00:10:37,240
I haven't retired yet.

172
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,960
Are you planning

173
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,200
to offend

174
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,720
all our fellow units?

175
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,000
No.

176
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,559
I'm just worried

177
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:48,679
you might recommend me

178
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,519
without my consent.

179
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:51,200
What if they accept me?

180
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:53,000
I can't keep working with you.

181
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,399
Don't worry, that won't happen.

182
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,919
Go back.

183
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,639
Alright then,

184
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,320
enjoy your tea.

185
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,039
I'm leaving.

186
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:12,360
If any unit needs people, I'll tell you.

187
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,360
I know what you're up to

188
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,960
just by the way you move.

189
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,360
Thank you, Chief.

190
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,720
Continue with your work.

191
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:26,624
Hello? Juvenile Correctional Facility.

192
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:28,879
Lu Sheng?

193
00:11:33,824 --> 00:11:34,592
Okay.

194
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,480
You, get up.

195
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:40,960
That's enough.

196
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,000
Come down now.

197
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,240
Please, okay?

198
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,240
Weixiang.

199
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,320
Stop running!

200
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,080
Weixiang!

201
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,279
Stop running!

202
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:53,120
Don't run.

203
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,200
You'll get hurt.

204
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,279
Stop running.

205
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,120
Don't kick.

206
00:12:06,799 --> 00:12:08,080
Watch him closely.

207
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:10,960
Come down. I'm exhausted...

208
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,320
Prosecutor Lin.

209
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,759
Let me do it.

210
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:14,879
Well,

211
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:17,120
anything needed, let's discuss later.

212
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,080
I haven't slept.

213
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,799
Look at this mess.

214
00:12:19,159 --> 00:12:20,440
No, we're here to help.

215
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:22,519
Didn't you notify us

216
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:24,120
to come for early intervention?

217
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,480
Xiaoyao!

218
00:12:26,848 --> 00:12:28,399
I let you call
the Juvenile Prosecution Office.

219
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:28,960
What is it?

220
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,039
Not the major crimes unit.

221
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,279
I did as you said.

222
00:12:34,048 --> 00:12:35,879
We're from Juvenile Prosecution Office.

223
00:12:39,399 --> 00:12:40,279
Where is Captain Du?

224
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:41,080
Captain Du?

225
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,080
In the interrogation room.

226
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,320
Stop crying, dear.

227
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,639
Contact the Welfare Home.

228
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:46,879
See if they can take them in.

229
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:47,320
Right now.

230
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,159
Alright.

231
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,080
You're too much!

232
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,360
Please, Prosecutor Lin.
We'll handle it.

233
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,440
I've been putting up with you
for quite some time.

234
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:55,639
- You, keep an eye on him.
- Okay.

235
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,240
Alright, kids.

236
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,879
Look what I've got.

237
00:13:01,639 --> 00:13:03,399
Who wants it?

238
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:05,240
Who behaves well can get it.

239
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,080
This time,

240
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:11,120
we caught one adult, six kids,

241
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,360
and one baby.

242
00:13:12,799 --> 00:13:14,360
You probably saw it all outside.

243
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,519
Where is that adult?

244
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,600
Well,

245
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,360
she's pregnant.

246
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,919
Once she got in,

247
00:13:23,919 --> 00:13:26,360
she said she's about to give birth,
forcing us to take her

248
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,240
to the hospital.

249
00:13:30,279 --> 00:13:32,240
This kid, an old acquaintance.

250
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:33,639
Just got released.

251
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:36,639
Can you reach their parents?

252
00:13:36,759 --> 00:13:37,679
No, we can't.

253
00:13:37,679 --> 00:13:38,960
Completely unreachable.

254
00:13:41,799 --> 00:13:42,720
Prosecutor Lin.

255
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:45,120
We've worked together
quite a few times, right?

256
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:46,039
This time,

257
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:47,559
Prosecutor Zheng said

258
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:49,480
you're exploring early intervention.

259
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,039
We're fully cooperating with you.

260
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,720
So, let's have a discussion.

261
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,120
As you know,

262
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,879
those kids outside

263
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,200
will have to be released.

264
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,799
Can we speed things up

265
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:02,080
and interrogate him first?

266
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:05,840
The guardian must be present.

267
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:07,120
Or we can't begin questioning.

268
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:09,559
You've all here.

269
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:10,679
You can supervise.

270
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,679
Early intervention

271
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,879
is different from
having a guardian present.

272
00:14:17,159 --> 00:14:19,120
You've handled major cases.

273
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:21,440
You know the importance
of timing, right?

274
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:24,720
Alright.

275
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,639
Nothing to hide.

276
00:14:26,639 --> 00:14:27,960
To be honest,

277
00:14:28,399 --> 00:14:29,240
this time,

278
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:31,360
we didn't catch them all.

279
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,120
We couldn't catch

280
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:35,279
the mastermind after a night waiting.

281
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:37,240
If we wait for another night,

282
00:14:37,639 --> 00:14:39,519
and that master behind runs away,

283
00:14:39,519 --> 00:14:41,279
all our efforts will be wasted.

284
00:14:43,808 --> 00:14:44,440
No way.

285
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,000
Just let me in.

286
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,088
- No.
- I'm his instructor.

287
00:14:49,088 --> 00:14:51,264
- No, there's no precedent.
- Come on, we are colleagues.

288
00:14:51,264 --> 00:14:52,200
See? I am a cop too.

289
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,200
Just let me in.

290
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,559
What's going on? Why yelling?

291
00:14:54,759 --> 00:14:55,600
Hello, sir.

292
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,799
I am Lu Sheng's instructor.

293
00:14:58,639 --> 00:15:00,120
Instructor Bai?

294
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,440
Prosecutor Lin.

295
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,639
You know each other?

296
00:15:03,039 --> 00:15:03,960
Kind of.

297
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,960
I know her.

298
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:06,759
She also knows me.

299
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,919
About last time, sorry.

300
00:15:09,919 --> 00:15:10,679
I was impulsive.

301
00:15:10,679 --> 00:15:11,600
About what?

302
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,240
Well, was a kid

303
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,519
named Lu Sheng

304
00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:17,919
arrested?

305
00:15:18,399 --> 00:15:19,960
You are his instructor, right?

306
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,080
Right.

307
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:24,639
Can you reach out to his parents?

308
00:15:25,039 --> 00:15:25,759
His parents...

309
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:26,840
What did he do?

310
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:29,080
I'm asking
if you can contact his parents.

311
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,440
Don't probe into the case.

312
00:15:30,879 --> 00:15:31,480
Can you?

313
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:32,559
His parents...

314
00:15:34,159 --> 00:15:35,200
Well, all the events

315
00:15:35,399 --> 00:15:37,559
we organized
that needed parents to attend,

316
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:38,399
he never showed up.

317
00:15:38,399 --> 00:15:39,519
When he left,

318
00:15:39,519 --> 00:15:40,879
we couldn't reach them either.

319
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,919
So what exactly did he do?

320
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,679
But, sir,

321
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:46,879
he has really reformed.

322
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:49,039
He was the class monitor,
even had sentence reduced.

323
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:50,200
He wouldn't mess up again.

324
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,720
Could there be some misunderstanding?

325
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:53,080
There's no misunderstanding.

326
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,799
He's caught red-handed with evidence.

327
00:15:55,399 --> 00:15:56,720
Can I go in and talk to him?

328
00:15:56,799 --> 00:15:57,759
I'll get what you

329
00:15:57,759 --> 00:15:58,759
want to know out of him.

330
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,000
Oh, you're that good?

331
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,559
Why not interrogate all other suspects?

332
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:03,759
Wait. Just trust me.

333
00:16:03,759 --> 00:16:06,039
He really listens to me.
I can definitely help you.

334
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:07,320
Let him in.

335
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,000
We need an appropriate adult present

336
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,879
as a legal representative.

337
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:14,080
Alright, I'm suitable.

338
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,679
Can you?

339
00:16:14,679 --> 00:16:15,440
I can do that.

340
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:15,879
Okay.

341
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:32,120
Kid, show some respect.

342
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,480
Today, we've invited colleagues

343
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:35,519
from the Procuratorate
just for your case,

344
00:16:35,879 --> 00:16:36,440
you got that?

345
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:36,879
Lu Sheng.

346
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:37,320
Here!

347
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:52,120
What did you say when being released?

348
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,960
Just nonsense?

349
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,480
Instructor Bai.

350
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:03,559
I haven't been to prison.

351
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:06,119
Don't shout at me so early.

352
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:07,359
You dare say that again!

353
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:08,119
Instructor Bai,

354
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:09,720
please take your seat.

355
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,079
Please sit down, okay? Come here.

356
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:16,640
You wait.

357
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,880
When it is over, I'll deal with you.

358
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:23,920
I'll just sit here.

359
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:26,359
Explain everything clearly!

360
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,000
Instructor Bai.

361
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:28,079
Your task today

362
00:17:28,079 --> 00:17:29,319
is just to observe.

363
00:17:31,119 --> 00:17:31,920
Do you understand?

364
00:17:35,079 --> 00:17:35,920
Lu Sheng, listen.

365
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:37,440
Since we cannot contact your parents,

366
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,200
according to the law,

367
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,359
we found an appropriate adult

368
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:41,279
to sit in and observe.

369
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,200
So many people, just for me?

370
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,079
Really?

371
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,880
No one will hurt you.
We're here to help you, okay?

372
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,160
- Okay.
- Let's begin.

373
00:17:50,848 --> 00:17:51,720
Let's begin.

374
00:17:53,079 --> 00:17:53,640
Lu Sheng.

375
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,279
Talk to us.

376
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,839
You've been here twice, huh?

377
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,680
You know the rules.

378
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,400
Just say what you want.

379
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,359
Kid, don't push your luck.

380
00:18:03,264 --> 00:18:03,960
Captain Du.

381
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,039
Keep the tone in check.

382
00:18:06,039 --> 00:18:07,319
He's still a minor.

383
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:09,680
- Okay?
- Alright.

384
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:18,079
Tell me, around 9 PM
on October 4th,

385
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:19,240
on Kexiang West Road,

386
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:21,319
you stole electric bike batteries.

387
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,359
Do you admit it?

388
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:23,519
I admit it.

389
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:24,672
Who organized it?

390
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:27,079
Who was the leader?

391
00:18:27,279 --> 00:18:27,840
I am.

392
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,519
You?

393
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:32,480
Then, how did you

394
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:33,319
know those kids?

395
00:18:33,559 --> 00:18:34,480
We met on the streets.

396
00:18:35,279 --> 00:18:35,920
All my buddies.

397
00:18:36,759 --> 00:18:38,759
Those seven or eight-year-olds?
Your buddies?

398
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,839
Those who crawl under the table

399
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:41,640
are your buddies?

400
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:42,880
Be serious.

401
00:18:43,039 --> 00:18:43,599
Right.

402
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,680
Do friends have age limits?

403
00:18:45,839 --> 00:18:46,640
Watch your attitude!

404
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:47,799
You too.

405
00:18:48,759 --> 00:18:49,519
You can't say.

406
00:18:54,279 --> 00:18:55,119
Let's all be serious.

407
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:57,680
Continue.

408
00:18:58,279 --> 00:18:58,799
Lu Sheng.

409
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,000
What made you think

410
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,319
of organizing these kids

411
00:19:02,319 --> 00:19:03,200
to commit theft?

412
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,200
None of us got parents.

413
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,039
We live together.

414
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,480
We have to eat and earn some money.

415
00:19:10,799 --> 00:19:13,559
What's your connection to Zhou Aijuan,
the pregnant woman?

416
00:19:14,279 --> 00:19:15,039
No connection.

417
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:17,319
Every line of work has peers.

418
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,079
You mean, you all met on the streets,

419
00:19:23,559 --> 00:19:25,359
and to survive,

420
00:19:25,599 --> 00:19:27,200
you decided to steal together?

421
00:19:27,808 --> 00:19:28,720
Isn't it obvious?

422
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:30,519
Where do you live?

423
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,079
No place.

424
00:19:35,839 --> 00:19:36,400
We wander.

425
00:19:38,559 --> 00:19:39,079
Lu Sheng.

426
00:19:41,759 --> 00:19:45,000
If someone is coercing you,
you don't need to worry or be afraid.

427
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,799
But if you want

428
00:19:47,799 --> 00:19:49,119
to take all the blame now,

429
00:19:49,519 --> 00:19:50,880
that's not a truthful confession.

430
00:19:51,519 --> 00:19:52,519
No one is coercing me.

431
00:19:54,319 --> 00:19:55,000
I told you I got

432
00:19:55,799 --> 00:19:56,559
nowhere to stay.

433
00:19:56,559 --> 00:19:57,640
I just live there, okay?

434
00:19:58,039 --> 00:19:58,559
Kid.

435
00:19:59,359 --> 00:20:01,359
I'll remind you of something.

436
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,240
You're seventeen years old, right?

437
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,880
If you obstruct the investigation,

438
00:20:06,599 --> 00:20:08,519
it'll delay your case.

439
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:09,640
Understand?

440
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,640
I just said

441
00:20:11,359 --> 00:20:12,240
I organized it.

442
00:20:12,359 --> 00:20:13,599
I'll take responsibility.

443
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:14,720
Arrest me if you want.

444
00:20:17,599 --> 00:20:18,440
So by your own words,

445
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:20,759
you're the leader
of this theft group, right?

446
00:20:21,079 --> 00:20:21,880
Then tell me,

447
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:22,839
where did you fence

448
00:20:22,839 --> 00:20:23,920
the stolen goods?

449
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:26,799
E-bike shops, phone stores, and so on.

450
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:27,720
Which shop?

451
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:28,519
The owner's name?

452
00:20:29,079 --> 00:20:30,200
I can't remember clearly.

453
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:31,759
Then, last time,

454
00:20:31,759 --> 00:20:32,799
what did you sell?

455
00:20:33,799 --> 00:20:35,440
How much was it? You spent it.

456
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,039
On what?

457
00:20:38,039 --> 00:20:39,079
E-bike batteries.

458
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:40,640
One hundred each.

459
00:20:41,119 --> 00:20:41,799
On food.

460
00:20:42,079 --> 00:20:42,784
What did you eat?

461
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:45,039
Barbecue.

462
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,839
Barbecue for a group of kids.

463
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,759
Is one hundred yuan enough?

464
00:20:50,279 --> 00:20:52,920
I can't remember the details.

465
00:20:53,559 --> 00:20:54,200
Forgot again?

466
00:20:55,119 --> 00:20:56,240
Didn't the owner ask you

467
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,440
where the battery came from?

468
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:58,720
No.

469
00:20:58,799 --> 00:20:59,880
Why not?

470
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:01,960
He knows us.

471
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:02,559
No need to ask.

472
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:04,200
Are you gonna keep lying?

473
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,359
Did I let you speak?

474
00:21:06,839 --> 00:21:07,880
Well, you don't know him.

475
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,880
Believe it or not!

476
00:21:09,599 --> 00:21:10,599
You are still lying?

477
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,119
Did I let you speak?

478
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,599
You know where we are?

479
00:21:13,632 --> 00:21:14,400
Get him out!

480
00:21:14,839 --> 00:21:16,640
You think I don't know you?
Speak the truth!

481
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:17,799
Get out, now.

482
00:21:18,119 --> 00:21:19,000
Wait for me, Lu Sheng.

483
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:19,680
Instructor Bai,

484
00:21:23,839 --> 00:21:25,079
you never know me.

485
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,480
When I came out, you told me

486
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:30,200
to start afresh.

487
00:21:31,079 --> 00:21:32,319
A man

488
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,720
must solve problems.

489
00:21:34,839 --> 00:21:35,680
But it's no use.

490
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,960
I'm just a maggot in the gutter.

491
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:40,039
Your teachings

492
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:41,519
are useless.

493
00:21:42,519 --> 00:21:44,119
- Talking nonsense!
- Lu Sheng.

494
00:21:44,119 --> 00:21:44,640
Take him out.

495
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:46,359
Now! Get him out!

496
00:21:46,359 --> 00:21:48,279
- I wasted two years on teaching you!
- Get out!

497
00:21:48,519 --> 00:21:49,880
Lu Sheng, you bad guy!

498
00:21:52,032 --> 00:21:52,839
Captain Du.

499
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:54,720
Can't continue. Let's go.

500
00:21:57,024 --> 00:21:57,799
Watch him.

501
00:21:59,839 --> 00:22:00,680
Prosecutor Lin.

502
00:22:01,359 --> 00:22:04,000
When did you transfer over
to handle juvenile cases?

503
00:22:04,759 --> 00:22:05,400
Not long ago.

504
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:07,880
The office just started
juvenile justice pilot department.

505
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,480
You got promoted?

506
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,864
- Not at all.
- How many people report to you?

507
00:22:13,559 --> 00:22:14,079
Just one.

508
00:22:15,359 --> 00:22:16,680
Just a clerk.

509
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,920
- That's it?
- That's it.

510
00:22:18,759 --> 00:22:20,400
How can you even manage?

511
00:22:21,799 --> 00:22:22,440
Captain Du.

512
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:25,480
For all future juvenile cases,

513
00:22:25,799 --> 00:22:28,279
we may need to intervene early

514
00:22:28,799 --> 00:22:29,799
to guide investigations.

515
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,559
We'll need your full cooperation.

516
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,079
Got it.

517
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:35,759
A pilot, after all.

518
00:22:35,759 --> 00:22:36,359
Exactly.

519
00:22:38,119 --> 00:22:40,559
You just said "all",

520
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:41,960
you mean...

521
00:22:42,559 --> 00:22:44,319
All crimes committed by minors

522
00:22:44,319 --> 00:22:46,680
and all crimes against minors.

523
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:51,039
Actually, the main purpose is to guide
investigation and evidence collection.

524
00:22:52,039 --> 00:22:52,799
In this way,

525
00:22:52,799 --> 00:22:54,200
we can ensure that the evidence

526
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,599
meets the prosecution standards.

527
00:22:57,599 --> 00:22:58,160
Right.

528
00:23:00,359 --> 00:23:02,640
Alright, we're old friends, right?

529
00:23:02,799 --> 00:23:04,240
We'll work together more.

530
00:23:04,599 --> 00:23:05,792
I won't see you off today.

531
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:09,200
Captain Du,
you really don't want to keep me longer.

532
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,279
Not at all.

533
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:11,359
I understand.

534
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,880
Our early intervention

535
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,680
probably messes with your usual work.

536
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:15,599
But I promise

537
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:16,640
we are here to help,

538
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,400
not cause trouble.

539
00:23:19,599 --> 00:23:20,319
Got it.

540
00:23:21,359 --> 00:23:22,920
Nothing else you want to say to me?

541
00:23:23,759 --> 00:23:24,920
Haven't you said everything?

542
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,920
Nothing important to tell?

543
00:23:27,599 --> 00:23:28,200
What to tell?

544
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:31,839
If it were just a theft case,

545
00:23:31,839 --> 00:23:33,640
you'd not get Procuratorate in, right?

546
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:38,079
Prosecutor Lin,

547
00:23:38,079 --> 00:23:39,920
the moment you showed up, I knew...

548
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,319
Lead the way.

549
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:42,119
Okay, let's go

550
00:23:42,119 --> 00:23:42,960
to my office.

551
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,960
Let's talk.

552
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:47,119
This is from July 15th.

553
00:24:00,039 --> 00:24:00,599
See?

554
00:24:08,519 --> 00:24:09,519
That's a pregnant woman.

555
00:24:10,839 --> 00:24:11,759
The kid is so small.

556
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:12,759
Just this small.

557
00:24:17,079 --> 00:24:17,720
Quite smoothly.

558
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,920
They acted quite smoothly.

559
00:24:19,319 --> 00:24:20,119
Indeed.

560
00:24:20,119 --> 00:24:21,119
They are providing cover.

561
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:22,359
Next one.

562
00:24:24,359 --> 00:24:26,079
(Welcome)
From the 20th day of last month.

563
00:24:27,799 --> 00:24:28,119
Look.

564
00:24:43,119 --> 00:24:44,920
Now, these kids

565
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:45,880
and this pregnant woman

566
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,079
are regulars at the police station now.

567
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:49,680
The officers can't do much.

568
00:24:50,279 --> 00:24:50,920
They can only

569
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:51,759
educate the kids.

570
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:54,079
The woman always pretended
to be pitiful,

571
00:24:54,079 --> 00:24:56,000
saying she didn't even know the kids.

572
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,039
And the kids' parents

573
00:25:00,039 --> 00:25:01,160
can't be reached at all?

574
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,920
Some can.

575
00:25:04,279 --> 00:25:06,039
But just in days
after they were taken home,

576
00:25:06,039 --> 00:25:07,839
they were caught for theft again.

577
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:09,720
Moreover,

578
00:25:10,079 --> 00:25:11,319
we have now discovered

579
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,279
more kids are getting involved

580
00:25:14,839 --> 00:25:16,559
in theft than before.

581
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:19,880
Thank you.

582
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,319
We'll keep in touch then.

583
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:22,039
Alright.

584
00:25:22,039 --> 00:25:22,440
