931
00:40:05,239 --> 00:40:06,719
Uncle Xiong must be Pan Xiong.

932
00:40:06,719 --> 00:40:08,559
Keep your voice down. Everyone can hear.

933
00:40:10,079 --> 00:40:11,280
He's really bold,

934
